snippet.textDisplay:
Since this particular rendition has a few improvisations from the original Lalon-geeti, I decided to jot down the lyrics as I heard them. 

(Satyaki) (Bangla)

Chatoko-praay ohornishi, Cheye aachhe kaalo shoshi (x2)
Aami hobo bole chorono-daashi
Hobo-o bole chorono-daashi
O ta hoy na kopaal gune (x2)
Aamar moner manusher-o sone (x2)
Milon hobe koto din-e (x2)
Aamar moner manush-ero sone (x2)

(Anupam) (Hindi)

Main wahan jaa chukaa hoon, Tu jahaan reh chukaa hai (x2)
Mere dil mein kahin tu chhupaa to nahin
Muskuraata hua tu yahin hai kahin
Dhundta phir raha ik nishaani teri
Mil bhi jaaye to poonchoo kahaani meri
Kisliye, kisliye, jee rahaan hoon yahaan

(Anupam) (Bangla)

Milon hobe koto din-e (x2)
O aamar moner manush-ero sone (x2)

(Satyaki) (Bangla)

Megher bidyut meghe jemon, Lukaale na paay onweshon (x2)
Aami kaala-re haaraye temon
Kaala-re haaraye temon
Oi roop heri e-dorpone (x2)
Aamar moner manush-ero sone (x2)

(Babul) (Hindi)

Milan paane ko main teraa
O milan paane ko main teraa
Jogi banke firoon dekh ban-ban mein
O jogi banke firoon dekh ban-ban mein
Mere mann mein rehne wale (x2)
Kabhi to aa mere pyase nainan mein
O kabhi to aa mere pyase nainan mein

(Satyaki) (Bangla)

Jokhon oi roop smoron-o hoy, Thaake na loko-lojjar bhoy (x2)
Lalon fokir bhebe bole sodaa

(Anupam) (Bangla)

Lalon fokir bhebe bole sodaa-i
Oi prem je kore se jaane

(Satyaki) (Bangla)

He oi prem
Je kore se jaane
Aamar moner maanush-ero sone (x2)
Milon hobe koto dine (x2)
Aamar moner maanush-ero sone (x2)
